# Changelog

## v1.0.0 — First public kernel

- Implemented PantheonOS Kernel v0.1 with:
  - StateVector (hash-chained state)
  - ThoughtObject (hash-chained event ledger)
  - ΣC invariant gate with weighted components
  - Pluggable daemons (Mirror, Hound)
- Added `pantheon-demo` CLI for local multi-model walkthrough.
- Published standalone ΣC gate as `solomon-coil`.
- Shipped offline continuity engine `pantheon-zero` for Orange Pi / Raspberry Pi.